      "span_text": "In contrast, Gutierrez-Vega et al. [CITATION_1] quote resolutions of the Brazilian Federal Council of Medicine and Regional Council of Medicine of the State of Rio de Janeiro, clearly imposing on medical practitioners the duty of providing blood transfusions, even against one's wishes, when the patient's life is at stake."
